# info
Александр Градский и группа Скоморохи — Сатиры
http://www.discogs.com/master/350082
Melodiya 1987 2LP С60 25479 003
Recorded 1980

Another vocal suite of AG based on strong poetry of Саша Чёрный (1880—1932) that time. I hope you'll find at least the first track interesting which was used as a soundtrack for sci-fi cartoon <a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PhN9HamfbuY">Перевал</a> (I am very impressed of that minute the track lasts there). I am not sure what a label I could stick to these tracks but it's much alike “progressive” it seems.

[alexander gradsky - teatr 1980.mp3]  (what the sound!)

[alexander gradsky - potomki 1980.mp3]  (drum breaks & progressive)

